# Ægir
[![Nexusmods](https://img.shields.io/badge/-nexusmods-222222?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://www.nexusmods.com)
[![Thunderstore](https://img.shields.io/badge/-thunderstore-222222?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://thunderstore.io)

> **Aegir** is a jötunn and a personification of the sea in Norse mythology.

This simple mod removes camera water clipping in godmode allowing players dig and build
 underwater without problems.
